# PunamIDE v2.0 Configuration
# These values are configured via the Settings UI (gear icon).
# API keys are stored securely using tauri-plugin-store in your OS app data directory.
#
# Supported Providers:
#   gemini  - Google Gemini (FREE)  — Get key: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
#   groq    - Groq (FREE)           — Get key: https://console.groq.com/keys
#   mistral - Mistral AI            — Get key: https://console.mistral.ai/api-keys
#   openai  - OpenAI (paid)         — Get key: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
#
# Default Models:
#   gemini  → gemini-2.0-flash
#   groq    → llama-3.1-70b-versatile
#   mistral → mistral-small-latest
#   openai  → gpt-4o-mini
#
# No .env file is needed — all config is managed through the app's Settings panel.
